Template_ID

- Unique identifier for the sofa template.
- Assigned manually.

Template_Name

- Name of the CAD sofa template.
- Taken from the Fusion model/template name.

Sofa_Type

- Type of sofa (Straight, L-shape, U-shape, etc.).
- Assigned manually or by the image processing module.

Seat_Count

- Number of seating positions.
- Assigned manually or detected by Module 2.

Overall_Length_mm

- Total length of the sofa.
- Derived from the L_mm of the "fabric cover" body (overall bounding box).

Overall_Depth_mm

- Total depth (front-to-back) of the sofa.
- Derived from the W_mm of the "fabric cover" body (overall bounding box).

Overall_Height_mm

- Maximum height of the sofa.
- Derived from the H_mm of the "fabric cover" body (overall bounding box).

Armrest_Height_mm

- Height of the armrest.
- Prototype Rule:
  max(H_mm of left/right_armrest_top\*) + H_mm of left/right_armrest_base.

Backrest_Height_mm

- Height of the visible backrest.
- Derived from H_mm of backrest_front.

Seat_Height_mm

- Height of the seating surface from the ground.
- Derived from max_y_mm of seat_top.

Seat_Width_mm

- Seat width parameter used for scaling in the prototype.
- Derived from W_mm of seat_top.

Seat_Depth_mm

- Seat depth parameter used for scaling in the prototype.
- Derived from H_mm of seat_front.

Seat_Configuration

- Indicates whether seat cushions are Jointed or Separate.
- Assigned manually.

Armrest_Frame_Material

- Material of the internal armrest frame.
- Assigned manually / manufacturer information.

Backrest_Frame_Material

- Material of the internal backrest frame.
- Assigned manually / manufacturer information.

Fabric_Material

- Upholstery fabric material.
- Assigned manually / manufacturer information.

Leg_Count

- Number of sofa legs.
- Assigned manually or counted from the CAD model.

Leg_Material

- Material of the sofa legs.
- Assigned manually / manufacturer information.

Notes

- Additional remarks about the template.
- Added manually.
